      <title>野村证券的 Fadlallah 表示，中东地区 IPO 需求强劲，将继续保持合理的供应量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-22/mideast-ipo-appetite-strong-will-continue-to-see-reasonable-supply-nomura-s-fadlallah</link>
