      <title>摩根大通称英镑上涨面临风险，因看涨押注创下纪录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/jpmorgan-says-pound-rally-at-risk-as-bullish-bets-hit-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司警告称，随着英镑看涨押注攀升至历史新高，英镑强劲的涨势可能面临回调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/jpmorgan-says-pound-rally-at-risk-as-bullish-bets-hit-record</guid>
