      <title>印度将放宽国有企业借贷和投资规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/india-to-ease-borrowing-investment-rules-for-state-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度计划取消对国有企业的一些限制，包括允许它们无需寻求政府许可即可借贷和投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/india-to-ease-borrowing-investment-rules-for-state-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 10:16:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
